{"tid":518366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯判囚】支持者庭外鬧裁判官「死差婆」","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T11:50:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2602c688966ebf2030a9f6d9ea5e533a9f9f31f","tid":518366,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180103/large/1514968708_d35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180103%2Flarge%2F1514968708_d35a.jpg&h=402b9cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於庭外支持者得悉朱經緯被判即時監禁3個月，有人在庭外大叫「狗官、殘害忠良、香港警察受盡屈辱」，更有人辱罵裁判官：「阿差」、「死差婆」。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄指，除了在庭內法律程序進行時喧嘩會有機會構成「藐視法庭」罪之外，因法院大樓以至街道上都是公眾地方，在這些地方喧嘩亦可招致「公眾地方行為不檢」罪。根據《公安條例》最高可判罰5,000元及監禁12個月。更甚者，倘若評論法官內容牽涉「你出街要小心啲」之類的威嚇，更有機會觸犯「刑事恐嚇」罪。<br />\n<br />\n陸偉雄評論近年有市民恣意批評非華裔法官之風，形容不應助長，每一位法官都受過專業訓練，判決時把專業知識套用在案件中，每項判決都有根據。陸指法庭是講理據的地方，「你話佢有錯，咪去上訴囉」，挑剔法官的種族除了對事態毫無幫助，更有機會令自己犯罪被控，希望市民保持冷靜及信任法庭工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57660493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57660493&d=tPtgdxispHM4pG8INjHj0YM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=dce70ddc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57660493&h=175d1954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180103/57660493</a>"},{"pid":"33f9dedf63d29c40ff08e333073de532ebb60fa8","tid":518366,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"屌，咁有無人做嘢吿佢地先得㗎？"},{"pid":"c8edfdd7b1855a1e6b550339393b60b340b37ee3","tid":518366,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n差婆係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c50c8ca678e8e73f0091dec61be2c3f63fb0707","tid":518366,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"死差佬"},{"pid":"d8dce2d282e1b41f7f4d3d0dbd2eb259b1e70359","tid":518366,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"想問係邊個拘捕朱經緯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}